## ðŸ”Ž Risiko Utama

| Risiko             | Deskripsi                                                                 | Dampak      | Mitigasi / Kontrol                | Evidence                   |
|--------------------|---------------------------------------------------------------------------|-------------|-----------------------------------|----------------------------|
| **Hallucination**  | Model menghasilkan output salah/tidak relevan.                           | Tinggi      | Human-in-the-loop, Prompt mgmt    | Prompt Management Policy   |
| **Model Drift**    | Performa model turun karena perubahan data lingkungan.                    | Tinggi      | Retraining pipeline, Monitoring   | Retraining Log, Eval Report |
| **Data Leakage**   | Informasi sensitif terekspos dalam output model.                          | Sangat Tinggi | PII Redaction, Access Control    | DPIA, Access Log           |
| **Bias & Fairness**| Output AI diskriminatif terhadap kelompok tertentu.                       | Tinggi      | Bias testing, Fairness metric     | Fairness Report, Model Card|
| **Security Threat**| Serangan adversarial atau manipulasi data input.                          | Sedang      | Red Teaming, Penetration Testing  | Red Teaming Report          |

